import React from 'react'
import { Box } from '@mui/material'

const Contacts = () => {
  return (
    <Box style={{backgroundColor:"#804780", color:"#fcfafc"}}>
      <Box>
      <input
              type="email"
              name="Email"
              placeholder="Email"
              autoComplete="off"
              required
            />
      </Box>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default Contacts
